From: Christian Walter <christian.walter@9elements.com>
Date: Sat, 8 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] ARM: dts: hpe-gxp: add video thumbnail and USB UDC nodes

Add device tree nodes for the GXP video thumbnail engine and USB
device controllers required for KVM-over-IP functionality:

- thumbnail video capture engine at 0xc0000500
- UDC group controller (udcg) syscon at 0x80400800
- Three USB device controller instances (udc0-udc2)

UDC allocation follows HPE convention:
  udc0: HID gadget (keyboard + mouse for KVM)
  udc2: reserved for virtual NIC (ECM)

Upstream-Status: Pending
Signed-off-by: Christian Walter <christian.walter@9elements.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/hpe/hpe-gxp.dts | 41 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 41 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/hpe/hpe-gxp.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/hpe/hpe-gxp.dts
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/hpe/hpe-gxp.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/hpe/hpe-gxp.dts
@@ -616,4 +616,45 @@ fanctrl: fan-controller@c1000c00 {
 			fan-shutdown-percent = <50>;
 		};

+		thumbnail: video@c0000500 {
+			compatible = "hpe,gxp-video-thumbnail";
+			reg = <0xc0000500 0x20>;
+			hpe,bits-per-pixel = <32>;
+		};
+
+		udcg: syscon@80400800 {
+			compatible = "hpe,gxp-udcg", "syscon";
+			reg = <0x80400800 0x200>;
+		};
+
+		udc0: usb@80401000 {
+			compatible = "hpe,gxp-udc";
+			reg = <0x80401000 0x1000>;
+			interrupts = <13>;
+			interrupt-parent = <&vic1>;
+			hpe,vdev-num = <0>;
+			hpe,num-flex-endpoints = <4>;
+			hpe,udcg = <&udcg>;
+		};
+
+		udc1: usb@80402000 {
+			compatible = "hpe,gxp-udc";
+			reg = <0x80402000 0x1000>;
+			interrupts = <13>;
+			interrupt-parent = <&vic1>;
+			hpe,vdev-num = <1>;
+			hpe,num-flex-endpoints = <4>;
+			hpe,udcg = <&udcg>;
+		};
+
+		udc2: usb@80403000 {
+			compatible = "hpe,gxp-udc";
+			reg = <0x80403000 0x1000>;
+			interrupts = <13>;
+			interrupt-parent = <&vic1>;
+			hpe,vdev-num = <2>;
+			hpe,num-flex-endpoints = <4>;
+			hpe,udcg = <&udcg>;
+		};
+
 		spifi1: spi@c0000280 {
--
2.53.0
